I can't knock Fresh and Easy, I just can't into this place.  The selection is fine, its somewhere in between a special grocery store and a chain super market.  You can get in and out fast but I just have never been a fan of the prepared foods which is one of their big products.  The prepared foods always have seemed bland in terms of taste, I have never experienced a problem with freshness of the food but it is difficult to find much on the healthier side of the spectrum.  Some of the dishes are down right scary when you read the nutritional facts.  It will get the job done in a pinch but otherwise look for me at TJ's.

